Text.val: Linked investment account of the security account
7274- Max. security accounts in product has been reached (Always max. 1)
7271- Currency not valid for cash account
7616- lifeCycleTargetDate required/not correct when use Life cycle (security account)
8097- Multiple applications for product are not allowed
Check whether the maximum number of optional accounts has been reached
In case of a new securities account always use the one and only available default,
for a new cash account the accountType from the request is used
For the securities account, get investment account default in case of no linked investment account in request
7273- Account does not exist as optional in default account
7274- Max optional accounts in product has been reached
7490- Defaults for more than one securities account

ExpSyntax.val: 'Number of accounts in product '&Trim(Str({0,704643080},'4'))&'. Max number of accounts in default '&Trim(Str({0,704643079},'4'))
